name: VO2max 5min #1
description:
After a good warm-up, prepare yourself for 1 set of 5 minute VO2max efforts. A well developed VO2max system will allow you to recover from high-intensity efforts faster and increase endurance. 



Be prepared; VO2max training requires motivation and focus from you.
